LYING AACR2 IN PAPUA NEW GUINEA LIBRARIES.     REVIEWS SOME OF THE DEBATE OF THE PAST FEW YEARS CONCERNING THE ANGLO-AMERICANCATALOGUING RULES (2ND EDITION); EXPLAINS SOME OF THE NEW RELATED TOOLS THATHAVE BEEN INTRODUCED AND ACCEPTED IN LIBRARIES THROUGHOUT THE ENGLISH-SPEAKINGWORLD; STRESSES THE IMPORTANCE OF AACR 2 FOR PAPUA NEW GUINEAN LIBRARIANS ANDLIBRARY USERS; AND URGES ALL LIBRARIES (ESPECIALLY THOSE WITH LARGE AND VERYSPECIALISED COLLECTIONS) TO ADOPT AACR 2